{"type": "article", "id": 24453, "title": "卫生棉包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-25T07:00:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 80, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702133441v1WNJdaZxgmYwkcC.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是为女生生理周期使用的棉塞而设计的包装，但它完全没有任何常见的少女粉红色调。棉塞的小袋子包装极具几何图形的线条感，很小巧，它另配有专门放棉塞的方形盒子，是纯黑色的，在简洁大方中凸显出优雅自然。这个项目的初衷是想为不发达地区的女性也带来方便，让她们在心理上不会觉得异样。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133438tbP9ZYcDxdJsO8wU.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.54351852\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133438DqcCbOgkjp8179hW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133439EBkl3W1CKwanfv8d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53333333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 188px; width: 375px; left: 520px; top: 1037px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133439PdBQy9humFZA30Ya.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50092593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133440dbqLH7aex8hPnG9Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702133440aLcJvQMVPWFIXSoT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}